Package: symbolicr
Title: Symbolic Regression Framework for R
Description: Find non-linear formulas that fits your input data. 
    You can systematically explore and memorize the possible formulas 
    and it's cross-validation performance, in an incremental fashion. 
    Two interoperable search functions are available: 
    `random.search` performs a random exploration, 
    `genetic.search` employs a genetic optimization algorithm, 
    `comb.search` combines best results of the two.
Version: 1.0.0
